# AI CEO™
## Your Virtual Executive Team for Building, Organizing & Growing Your Business

AI CEO™ is an AI-powered business growth platform designed to help entrepreneurs, creators, nonprofits, and small business owners plan, organize, and grow their vision without needing to hire an entire executive team.

---

# 🚀 Features

## Free CEO Assessment
Users receive:
- CEO Growth Assessment
- Business Clarity Review
- Starter Action Plan
- AI Business Prompts

---

## AI CEO™ Blueprint ($49 One-Time)

Customers receive:
- Personalized 90-Day Business Blueprint
- Growth Roadmap
- Marketing Strategy Starter
- Operations Checklist
- CEO Workbook

---

## AI CEO™ Pro ($19/month)

Members receive:
- Monthly CEO Reviews
- Marketing Planning Tools
- Money Management Tools
- Operations Planning
- New AI Resources

---

## AI CEO™ Teams ($99/month)

Organizations receive:
- Team Dashboard
- SOP Builder
- Business Systems Library
- Organization Planning
- Growth Support Tools

---

# 🧠 How It Works

1. Customer completes the CEO Assessment
2. AI CEO™ analyzes their goals, skills, challenges, and growth needs
3. Customer receives a personalized business roadmap
4. Customers can upgrade into ongoing CEO support tools

